5010101.name: The Phantom Butterfly Begins
5010101.tips: The Phantom Butterfly effect continued to spread. Even Admin was troubled by it and saw black butterflies fluttering about...

5010102.name: Quake Rescue
5010102.tips: A Quake struck the Duskfall Area of Ain Soph. Shu dispatched a rescue team, with Admin leading a group of Modifiers.

5010103.name: The Undertaker
5010103.tips: Arriving in the disaster zone, the team noticed someone acting weirdly. They decided to investigate.

5010104.name: The Butterfly Returns
5010104.tips: Recovering back in the shelter, Admin dreamed of the black butterfly, then met Hel once more...

5010105.name: Bed of White Flowers
5010105.tips: When Admin and Hel traveled to the location given by the butterfly, they found a girl waiting for them.

5010106.name: Appointment
5010106.tips: Vena's spirit appeared and asked them to protect the girl. But there seemed to be something going on between her and Hel...

5010107.name: Recurring Dream
5010107.tips: Hel dreamed a long dream of the past...

5010108.name: Midnight Chat
5010108.tips: Hel struggled with memories after the reappearance of her sister and was reassured by Vina. But soon she received news that Vina was gravely ill.

5010109.name: Corruption
5010109.tips: On their way to obtain medicine, the two learned the refuge had come under Visbane attack and Vina was missing...

5010110.name: Tracks
5010110.tips: Learning that the doctor may have taken Vina, Admin and Hel returned to an already-searched graveyard in search of clues and found something.

5010111.name: The Truth
5010111.tips: A hidden door led them to an underground laboratory. A terminal they found seemed to have some information...

5010112.name: The Experiment Begins
5010112.tips: They finally reached the core area, but the experiment was already starting.

5010113.name: Hidden Scar
5010113.tips: The experiment failed and Hel was left in a coma. In the depths of her consciousness she met the nightmare that had been haunting her.

5010114.name: Partners
5010114.tips: The Visbanes in the lab started to fight. The team was hard pressed, and then Hel awakened...

5010115.name: New Family
5010115.tips: Things paused, but did not end.

5010116.name: Whistling Wind
5010116.tips: Hermes, on a supply mission, joined the rescue team and made good use of her skills.

5010117.name: Data-gathering
5010117.tips: Ookuninushi gave Hermes a data-gathering mission, and hoped she would use her speed to her advantage...

5010118.name: Lost Objects
5010118.tips: Hermes was working tirelessly in the refuge when a girl came to ask for help.

5010119.name: Tracking Coordinates
5010119.tips: On obtaining the coordinates, Hermes found...

5010120.name: Strange Room
5010120.tips: Hermes followed the tracks underground, where she found a strange room.

5010121.name: Race
5010121.tips: To protect the important things to her, Hermes decided to stop the collapse of Sephirah Zone.

5010122.name: Rest
5010122.tips: Sometimes it is not bad to take some rest.

5020101.name: Memory: Sheep
5020101.tips: "So long as the sheep does not hear the words of the fox," Osiris thought after hearing this story.

5020102.name: Dream Negotiations
5020102.tips: In order to awaken Osiris' consciousness, the Administrator and Ausar made a wager to enter the dreamworld...

5020103.name: Imago Room
5020103.tips: Admin finally met Osiris in her Imago Room, but she is still unwilling to return to reality. The little Sheep with its open wounds locks itself within the room in its heart.

5020104.name: Facing Oneself
5020104.tips: "I will no longer use Ausar as an excuse. I must return to my friends, and thus... I will defeat you, Osiris."

5020105.name: A Bitter Battle
5020105.tips: Ver and Shu saved the Administrator in time. Soon after they faced the raving attacks of Ausar. But just then... the girl liberated herself and rushed to the battlefield.

5020106.name: The Sheep's Conclusion
5020106.tips: Osiris wrote a new ending to the fairy tale, just as she made a new decision concerning her future.

5030101.name: The Strange Beach
5030101.tips: The team may have survived a shipwreck, but they then had to face a beach teeming with unknown dangers.

5030102.name: A Miracle Named Snowflake 2
5030102.tips: Skadi's call was really answered, perhaps miracles do exist.

5030103.name: The Captain's Sleepless Night
5030103.tips: The team finally wrested Snowflake 2 from the Visbanes' grasp, but Skadi still seems preoccupied with something.

5030104.name: Target: The Next Island
5030104.tips: Skadi announced that the team was stranded on a deserted island and must embark on a necessary adventure.

5030105.name: The Strange Reunion
5030105.tips: As Leviathan finally neared the part she was tasked with finding, she also got closer to that mysterious sound.

5030106.name: Crisis, as Promised
5030106.tips: As the island tremors and a large number of Visbanes converge on the rendezvous point, Leviathan is nowhere to be found...

5030107.name: The Final Dash
5030107.tips: Leviathan didn't abandon her mission. In fact, the rendezvous point is just up ahead.

5030108.name: Skadi's Resolution
5030108.tips: Skadi is determined to rescue Leviathan, whatever the cost.

5030109.name: Waking Moment
5030109.tips: When everyone wakes in the afternoon between lessons, it's as if the adventure never even happened.

5030110.name: The Ocean Floor's Secret
5030110.tips: Having seen through the illusion, everyone arrives at the bubble world at the bottom of the sea, where they will face a new danger.

5030111.name: The Price of Charging Ahead
5030111.tips: After arriving in the new bubble at Skadi's recommendation, everyone immediately realizes that this was a risky decision.

5030112.name: Siren's Return
5030112.tips: The Siren has returned and sealed the way out. If the team wants to flee for our lives, they must fight to the death!

5030113.name: Leviathan's Confusion
5030113.tips: When Leviathan wakes again, she's still carrying out a mission with her Master, only nothing about it seems real.

5030114.name: The Trial That Must Be Cleared
5030114.tips: Leviathan finally understands that the one before her isn't her Master, but rather something that must overcome.

5030115.name: My Name Is Labbi
5030115.tips: Leviathan obtained a new Access Key and faces a new danger.

5030116.name: A Worthy Heroine
5030116.tips: Aided by the power of her new Access Key, Leviathan successfully rescued the Administrator. At the same time, she also made some kind of decision.

5030117.name: Countertide Whalesong
5030117.tips: The investigation team has assembled again, and this time, they won't back down!

5030118.name: Summer Will Eventually Fade
5030118.tips: Monsters, deserted islands, illusions... They all dissipate into the sea, and only memories remain of this summer.

5050101.name: Convallaria Selections
5050101.tips: The nine-year-old Athena took part in the selections run by the Knights of Convallaria for the very first time.

5050102.name: Determined
5050102.tips: Despite being told that there was an additional test after having passed both the written and battlefield parts of the selection, Athena accepted the challenge without complaint.

5050103.name: An Unexpected Trial
5050103.tips: Athena, who had entered Stellaris Temple alone, was attacked by the newly installed AGI Mecha guarding the temple which failed to recognize her.

5050104.name: Unmarked on the Map
5050104.tips: Athena, who was being pursued by the AGI Mecha, found herself in a room that she had never seen before on the map. There, she met a sculptor who was hard at work.

5050105.name: The Uncompleted Gift
5050105.tips: It turned out that the sculptor was a friend of Colleen Pallas, Athena's grandmother, who had borrowed the Pallas family treasure to create a gift for Colleen.

5050106.name: In a Race With Time
5050106.tips: The sculptor was becoming visibly weaker. However, he continued to work as hard as he can to try and complete the gift he had promised.

5050107.name: Athena's Promise
5050107.tips: Seeing that the artist had become weak, the Visbane hiding in the mirror launched its attack. To protect the artist and his work, Athena wielded her sword against a mighty foe.

5050108.name: It's Finally Over
5050108.tips: Athena's incredible journey came to an end with the delivery of the completed sculpture as promised.

5050109.name: The Youngest-Ever Knight
5050109.tips: As people were anxiously waiting for her outside, Athena finally emerged from the temple. She was now indisputably the youngest-ever person to become a Knight of Convallaria.

5050110.name: Immortal Star in Thy Eyes
5050110.tips: Athena delivered the statue to her grandmother, and conveyed a message from the sculptor.

5060101.name: Secret Deal
5060101.tips: Late in the night, the Akkadian Guild's second in command, Kingu, spoke with a mystery person, then decided what he must do.

5060102.name: The Rebellion
5060102.tips: The Akkadian Guild was under heavy assault by those who called themselves the Resistance. Marduk arrived on the scene to the relief of the besieged. Marduk didnt tolerate betrayal from anyone, not even his own family.

5060103.name: Stealthy Shadow
5060103.tips: In a container zone far from the battle front, Anubis received an order that had come from Paracaesar herselfhe must complete a top-secret infiltration mission as soon as possible.

5060104.name: The Dilemma
5060104.tips: Father and son, facing off against each other in what was a complicated situation, made their respective choices. The difference in experience and drive between them would ultimately determine the outcome of the battle.

5060105.name: Turning the Tide
5060105.tips: Marduk forced Kingu to show his trump card, but it came at a hefty cost.

5060106.name: The Dark Metal Menace
5060106.tips: To cover his men's retreat, Marduk took the greatest risk.

5060107.name: The Jackal's Choice
5060107.tips: Paracaesar finally issued a new order. However, Anubis must consider the price of carrying out this order.

5060108.name: An Unexpected Encounter
5060108.tips: Anubis came to the Rostach Drinkery to receive his punishment from Paracaesar. There someone unexpected was waiting for him.

5060109.name: Jack of Hearts
5060109.tips: To find out where Marduk was, Bastet must engage Jack in a "card game" and win.

5060110.name: King of the Ring
5060110.tips: The clue pointed to a legendary fighter in the container zone, and there was only one way to extract information from a man like this.

5060111.name: Buried Deep
5060111.tips: Following the information they had been given, Anubis and Bastet located an old record treasured by Marduk. The record contained a shocking secret.

5060112.name: Skulking in the Night
5060112.tips: Bastet and Anubis sneaked into the forbidden zone where Marduk was, both to complete the mission and to uncover the truth.

5060113.name: Project Graytower
5060113.tips: Marduk recounted his memories of Project Graytower, disclosing a painful truth...

5060114.name: Resistance HQ
5060114.tips: Kingu, who was busy recruiting new blood, learned about Marduk's escape and decided to lead the pursuit himself. At the same time, Bastet, Anubis, and Marduk had no choice but to fight.

5060115.name: Copper Duel I
5060115.tips: Reinforcements from the Akkadian Guild arrived in the nick of time, and father and son were once again facing off against each other on the battlefield.

5060116.name: Copper Duel II
5060116.tips: Kingu was intractable, and Anubis finally decided to intervene in this duel between father and son.

5060117.name: Resolve and Resilience
5060117.tips: The sudden Quake resulted in countless casualties, yet Kingu had to continue fulfilling his duty.

5060118.name: Order and Defiance
5060118.tips: Anubis once again got in touch with Paracaesar, and finally learned about of her cold-blooded plan.

5060119.name: A Father's Resolve
5060119.tips: Marduk saved the careless Kingu but sustained a severe injury in the process. This time round, he was determined to do the right thing as a father.

5060120.name: Father and Son
5060120.tips: Though thoroughly bruised and battered, Marduk finally did what a father must do.

5060121.name: Infiltration
5060121.tips: As the bounty hunter was locked in a fierce battle with the Resistance, Sobek arrived at a hidden warehouse on an "infiltration" mission.

5060122.name: The Underground Factory
5060122.tips: Sobek discovered an underground factory beneath the warehouse, where he uncovered an unimaginable secret...

5060123.name: Urgent Retreat
5060123.tips: Sobek accidentally triggered the alarm and had to make a run for it.

5060124.name: Project Dark Metal
5060124.tips: Ethan learned the secret behind Dark Metal from the lab logs brought out by Sobek.

5060125.name: Codename 0704
5060125.tips: As the hand pulling the strings of the Rostach incident, Paracaesar seemed to have another more important plan...

5060701.name: Act I: Opposition
5060701.tips: With the Salon near at hand, a girl named Chloe arrives at the Society of Muses hoping to have her fireworks certified.

5060702.name: Act I: Prologue
5060702.tips:
Hera's Battle Record I
"The elegance of the world cannot be concealed by a brief period of confusion."

5060703.name: Act II: Embers Igniting
5060703.tips: After receiving Hera's rejection, Chloe brings her works to the Fireworks Guild, but she is taken advantage of by the Fact-Finding Committee.

5060704.name: Act II: Interlude
5060704.tips:
Hera's Battle Record II
"Some make waves, others make sacrifices."

5060705.name: Act III: Flames Devouring
5060705.tips: During the Salon, Chloe's fireworks unexpectedly explode during the performance. Hera uses her Access Key to disperse the flames and prevent casualties.

5060706.name: Act III: Interlude
5060706.tips:
Hera's Battle Record III
"I pick up the hues the stars paint the earth."

5060707.name: Act IV: A Call in the Night
5060707.tips: Chloe is rejected by the Fact-Finding Committee. In desperation, Leuce, the maid of the Society of Muses, went to her...

5060708.name: Act IV: Interlude
5060708.tips:
Hera's Battle Record IV
"Radiance does not beget greatness, nor prosperity brilliance."

5060709.name: Act V: What the Beginning Felt Like
5060709.tips: Hera instructs Chloe in how to approach and pursue art. Awakened to the truth, Chloe delves back into the art of fireworks.

5060710.name: Act V: Interlude
5060710.tips:
Hera's Battle Record V
"People can always find their way towards the light in the darkness of night."

5060711.name: Fin: Dawn Star
5060711.tips: With the Salon postponed due to the accident, Hera appears with Chloe's new works, rehabilitating Chloe's name and making her works a huge success.

5060712.name: Fin: Epilogue
5060712.tips:
Hera's Battle Record VI
"Even if the night is long, dawn lies ahead."

5080101.name: Fire at the Mansion
5080101.tips: A puzzling fire drew the attention of Odin. The Valleyrand Family was in the midst of a major upheaval.

5080102.name: Fire Scene
5080102.tips: Ordered to the scene of the fire to uncover the truth, Heimdall meets someone unexpected there.

5080103.name: Tyr Valleyrand
5080103.tips: Two Modifiers of dramatically different positions made their identities known to each other, and embarked on a new partnership.

5080104.name: Family
5080104.tips: Tyr wasn't able to awaken Tyrfing's power, but he seems determined to fight something.

5080105.name: Partners Contingent
5080105.tips: Tyr and Heimdall officially began working together, and would soon come upon an astonishing discovery.

5080106.name: Firebrand Space
5080106.tips: The blazing room rouses the pain in Tyr's heart, but he's not about to give up.

5080107.name: Hell Hound
5080107.tips: The fierce battle finally gave the two the data they were seeking. However, irreconcilable differences also meant that their provisional partnership was at an end.

5080108.name: Promises and Lies
5080108.tips: Finally returning to a home where he can rest at ease, he reflects on some memories before setting off once again.

5080109.name: Fruitless Investigation
5080109.tips: Heimdall reopens her investigation, but all it leads her to is a dead endShe's no closer to finding the answers to her questions.

5080110.name: Burning Vengeance
5080110.tips: The nephew and unclewho have long contented against each other on the battlefield of businessfinally meet. This time, the more determined of the two has the upper hand.

5080111.name: Ray of Hope
5080111.tips: Heimdall goes to the Valleyrands' new apartment. She doesn't find Tyr there, but she does come to a startling conclusion.

5080112.name: Fiery Showdown
5080112.tips: With the help of the being he despises, Tyr finally gets his revenge. Now it's time for him to fulfill his mission.

5080113.name: A New Era
5080113.tips: The potential disaster was quelled at last, paving the way for what was a destined partnership.

5100101.name: Thoughts Over Tea
5100101.tips: According to a program on TV, the stock price of Tian Lu Traders had plummeted, and its president had resigned to take responsibility for this occurrence.Gengchen watched the program without saying a word, though Lingguang could sense her agitation and asked her if she wanted to go see Luliang, whom she hadn't seen for many years.

5100102.name: Yu Jing Memories
5100102.tips: Luliang thought back to the days when she could have a meal with Gengchen and the two of them would talk about their dreams and how they would help each other. But now... it looked like she couldn't even hold on to Tian Lu Traders any longer...

5100103.name: Images of Days Past
5100103.tips: Luliang returned to the streets where she grew up, feeling lost. However, the sight of the bustling street gave her new motivation. She entered a gallery where her eyes fell on a painting titled "Along the Luo River"...

5100104.name: Reunion
5100104.tips: It was as if the two of them had just met the day before. Gengchen brought a valuable bottle of liquor to cheer Luliang up, and the latter invited her to watch a magic show called "Business."

5100105.name: So-Called "Businessperson"
5100105.tips: Seeing that Luliang was in good spirits, Gengchen planned to make her way back to the Quad. However, due to Luliang's pestering, she eventually decided to spend another afternoon with her. Along the way, she found herself cheered up by the hustle and bustle of Xu Heng as well...

5100106.name: Along the Luo River
5100106.tips: In the final scene of "magic show," Luliang brought Gengchen to the gallery where she gifted "Along the Luo River" to Gengchen. This painting illustrates your wish, Luliang said.

5100107.name: Return
5100107.tips: Luliang returned to Tian Lu Traders with a gift for Yingzhao, the "head butler", as well as a grand present for everyone: a declaration from an alliance of small and medium businesses in Xu Heng for the titans.

5110101.name: And So Lie The Mountain and Rivers
5110101.tips: Yingzhao comes to Nanjiao Isle to take on San Ding Group as a representative of Tian Lu Traders, but she receives an unexpected message from her sister Linyu requesting help.

5110102.name: This and That
5110102.tips: Yingzhao runs into Jinwu at Mount Xiaoyang, and the two of them carry the comatose Linyu down the mountain. After safely placing Linyu in a nearby workshop, Yingzhao heads out alone to investigate.

5110103.name: Competing Concerns
5110103.tips: San Ding Group has used disgraceful tactics in the past to get its way, but there could be Visbanes on Mount Xiaoyang. Yingzhao has no choice but to put aside the business dispute for now and accompany Jinwu back into the mountains to investigate.

5110104.name: Problem To Be Solved
5110104.tips: Yingzhao and Jinwu venture deep into Mount Xiaoyang. Fighting shoulder to shoulder, they slowly get to know each other better. Little do they know, San Ding Group has something up their sleeve.

5110105.name: Tableau Crisis
5110105.tips: Yingzhao and Jinwu discover that the barrier "Ruomu Tableau" that suppresses "Chaos" has loosened, and they encounter two very strong Visbanes. After fighting them back, they head to Mount Dayang to seach for Xihe, hoping she can help strengthen the barrier.

5110106.name: Of Chivalry
5110106.tips: Though Yingzhao did not manage to meet Xihe, during her conversation with Jinwu she became moved by the latter's pure dream of becoming a hero. The two ran into Mengzhang, who came bearing bad news...

5110107.name: Realm of Imago
5110107.tips: The conflict between San Ding Group and the Nanjiao Isle workshop owners reached its peak. To save the workshop owners who had entered Mount Xiaoyang, Yingzhao fought with the inner demon released by Chaos. In the end, she was able to rescue them safely.

5110108.name: Inside and Outside
5110108.tips: San Ding Group's development of the mountains broke the barrier. Yingzhao, Jinwu and Mengzhang worked together to rescue others and combat the Visbanes. Yingzhao risked her life to maintain the barrier and was rescued by Xihe just before she collapsed.

5110109.name: So Should The Mountain And Rivers Be
5110109.tips: Xihe suppressed Chaos and Mount Xiaoyang was at peace once again. Jinwu returned with Xihe to Ruomu Palace for training, while Yingzhao continued on with her business dealings...

5110110.name: A Trip Worthwhile
5110110.tips: Two days prior. Mengzhang came to Mount Dayang to visit Xihe, and spoke of certain secrets that were unknown at the time.

5210101.name: Memory: Sheep
5210101.tips: "So long as the sheep does not hear the words of the fox," Osiris thought after hearing this story.

5210102.name: Dream Negotiations
5210102.tips: In order to awaken Osiris' consciousness, the Administrator and Ausar made a wager to enter the dreamworld...

5210103.name: Battle Incepted 1
5210103.tips: The two linked to the dream together. The Administrator proposed covertly cutting off the operation of AGI Mecha Legion, which was scorned by Ausar, who chose to confront it directly instead.

5210104.name: Battle Incepted 2
5210104.tips: The two linked to the dream together. The Administrator proposed covertly cutting off the operation of AGI Mecha Legion, which was scorned by Ausar, who chose to confront it directly instead.

5210105.tips: The two linked to the dream together. The Administrator proposed covertly cutting off the operation of AGI Mecha Legion, which was scorned by Ausar, who chose to confront it directly instead.

5210112.tips: The two linked to the dream together. The Administrator proposed covertly cutting off the operation of AGI Mecha Legion, which was scorned by Ausar, who chose to confront it directly instead.

5210113.name: Battle Incepted 11
5210113.tips: The two linked to the dream together. The Administrator proposed covertly cutting off the operation of AGI Mecha Legion, which was scorned by Ausar, who chose to confront it directly instead.

5210114.name: Imago Room
5210114.tips: Admin finally met Osiris in her Imago Room, but she is still unwilling to return to reality. The little Sheep with its open wounds locks itself within the room in its heart.

5210115.name: Facing Oneself
5210115.tips: "I will no longer use Ausar as an excuse. I must return to my friends, and thus... I will defeat you, Osiris."

5210116.name: A Bitter Battle
5210116.tips: Ver and Shu saved the Administrator in time. Soon after they faced the raving attacks of Ausar. But just then... the girl liberated herself and rushed to the battlefield.

5210117.name: The Sheep's Conclusion
5210117.tips: Osiris wrote a new ending to the fairy tale, just as she made a new decision concerning her future.

5170101.name: Looking Back
5170101.tips: The diary, once covered in dust, has been opened once again. What should one write on its pages that have not seen a new word in a while?

5170102.name: Moonchase
5170102.tips: As the moon in the distant sky gradually disappears, the shadow gets closer and closer to the person looking at themselves in the water's reflection.

5170103.name: Creeping Misfortune
5170103.tips: The blue sky disappears as dark clouds roll in. The shower that soon materializes is but the prelude to the rainy season.

5170104.name: Ready to Fly
5170104.tips: When only the embers of one's hopes and ideals remain, should the broken soul grasp at imperfect salvation?

5170105.name: Preliminary Exploration
5170105.tips: A faint lamp has illuminated the dark abyss for the first time, tearing open the veil on the hidden conspiracy within.

5170106.name: Working in Collusion
5170106.tips: The clues are about to emerge, and the capture is imminent. Act nowthe thief is already in our grasp.

5170107.name: Dangerous Order
5170107.tips: The hunter has become the hunted. Those who are already in the game have no other way out but to continue forging their way forward.

5170108.name: One Trouble After Another
5170108.tips: A dangerous encirclement has formed in the dark night. Now, the only things one can rely on are the flashing sword and the one whose hand is holding on to yours.

5170109.name: Calamity
5170109.tips: Fire is pouring down from the sky where the giant statue looms motionlessly. In this great disaster, the birds flying side by side cast the tiniest of shadows.

5170110.name: Manpower
5170110.tips: A brilliant light pierces the dark, silent night. The flaming bird is like a meteor, falling towards the hope behind the iron wall.

5170111.name: Protection
5170111.tips: The long night is about to pass. The dawn bursts out of the horizon, but the last swordsman falls before dawn.

5170112.name: Bright Moon
5170112.tips: "You have days so beautiful that they sadden you, and your demise is even more beautiful."

5170113.name: Fading Light of Life
5170113.tips: The white bird has fallen, but the moonlight remains gentle, illuminating new joys and sorrows day after day.

5170114.name: New Life
5170114.tips: Breaking free from the shackles for the first time and rediscovering where one's heart will lead to in this crumbling world.

5170115.name: Resource
5170115.tips: The line between antique and junk is often a fine one. The pursuit of past value is always a risky endeavor given hindsight. Every second counts in efforts to save forgotten treasure.

5170116.name: Interests Coincidental
5170116.tips: Tempting treasures will never attract just one hunter, and when several hunters all want to have a piece of the same pie, how to go about temporary partnership is the question.

5170117.name: Cover Up
5170117.tips: The treasure is being watched over by guards vigilant. The hunter who acts rashly will only fall into danger. Only by relying on flexible strategies can they get away for the time being.

5170118.name: Crossing Swords
5170118.tips: Simply escaping will not help one to get their hands on the treasure. If wit is not the way here, the hunter will be left with only one choice.

5170119.name: Captive
5170119.tips: The treasure hunter has made their way in to the mysterious treasure. However, the glittering light in front of them often masks the danger that awaits.

5170120.name: Rescue
5170120.tips: Rules cannot determine the boundary between good and evil. The sinner who acts alone receives salvation from man.

5170121.name: All Square
5170121.tips: Whether it be about one's interests or the spiritual standards, once the weights are placed on the scales, the deal can be struck.

5170122.name: Restart
5170122.tips: When the existing order remains deaf to the cries of the people, confused souls will always find a new way out.

5170123.name: Blank Slate
5170123.tips: A blank past means loss, while a blank future represents new life.

5170124.name: Lost Wish
5170124.tips: Although the distant memories have been forgotten, certain things continue at a slow burn. As long as there is a sliver of desire, courage will not be lost.

5170125.name: Brand New Chapter
5170125.tips: New words on a new page. The gears of destiny begin to turn fitfully.

5180102.name: An encounter in the White Night Gallery.
5180102.tips: Oneiroi has visited this gallery in the past, but it didn't look like this.

5180103.name: Return to the dream house
5180103.tips: Oneiroi went back home of her own volition... Is that really what happened?

5180104.name: Off Again
5180104.tips: Leave here, right now. This isn't home.

5180105.name: Mr. Cookie
5180105.tips: You've gotta get out of here. This isn't the dream you remember.

5180106.name: Mama Sheep and the Brave Little Lamb
5180106.tips: Mama Sheep found her baby, and Oneiroi found something that only she can do.

5180108.name: Farewell
5180108.tips: Ms. Puppet is fed up with being a burden.

5180109.name: The Robot and the Thinking Module
5180109.tips: If you install a Thinking Module in a robot, does it become even more like a robot, or even more like a human?

5180110.name: Finding Yourself
5180110.tips: Where did you come from, and where do you want to go?

5180112.name: Evil Presence
5180112.tips: Evil has been defeated, and the story has reached its end.

5180113.name: Waking From a Long Dream
5180113.tips: Oneiroi doesn't want to forget this story. Luckily, she's a skilled artist, so she can draw the story to help her remember it.

5140101.name: The Slums of Shashvat
5140101.tips: Luwu's investigation into the illegal substance takes her to the slums of Shashvat, where she receives a "warm welcome" from the locals.

5140102.name: Missing Persons
5140102.tips: Luwu follows Kali to Meruism, where she receives dreadful news before the investigation has even begun.

5140103.name: Police Story
5140103.tips: The Slums' public security system exists in name only. Rather than offering Luwu any assistance, it becomes an obstacle to her investigation.

5140104.name: The Last Bullet
5140104.tips: Luwu and Kali proceed to Vimoksha Pharma to investigate a missing persons case.

5140105.name: Quagmire
5140105.tips: After acquiring intel from Meruism, Luwu breaks up an illegal Panthera trade.

5140106.name: A Sleepless Night
5140106.tips: Following the clues, Luwu sneaks into Vimoksha Pharma in the dead of night in search of Zhiming and the illegal substance.

5140107.name: A Determined Mind
5140107.tips: Luwu confirms the source of the illicit substance through Kumar. Meanwhile, a gang fight breaks out in Meruism.

5140108.name: Fists and Firearms
5140108.tips: Ravana, the leader of Panthera, looks like someone that shouldn't be trifled with. There may not be a way to settle this dispute.

5140109.name: Quad Signal
5140109.tips: The explosion in the outskirts of town hint at more clues. Luwu asks an old friend for assistance, but it doesn't go well.

5140110.name: Crossing the Line
5140110.tips: Luwu conducts a lone rescue, but runs into a formidable adversary.

5140111.name: Luwu's Spear
5140111.tips: As Luwu finds herself in a dangerous situation, things turn around slightly following a mishap in the Vimoksha Pharma building.

5140112.name: Chaotic Battle
5140112.tips: Luwu breaks into the building. The conspiracy in Vimoksha Pharma is revealed, and helping hands arrive from all over to save the day.

5140113.name: So-called Justice
5140113.tips: The suspected biological weapons maker is about to escape, and Luwu chooses to enact her own form of justice.

5140114.name: Wrong Moment
5140114.tips: Zhiming comes to Shashvat on a job from Gengchen and stops briefly in Meruism to wait for Brahm.

5140115.name: A Strange Occurrence
5140115.tips: Zhiming is anxious to return to Xu Heng after hearing about an accident on Mount Jingdu, but she runs into trouble after going out to look for Brahm.

5140116.name: Silver Lining
5140116.tips: Her Access Key destroyed, Zhiming is held captive inside Vimoksha Pharma and forced to help Seema research biological weapons.

5140117.name: Vengeance and Destruction
5140117.tips: Zhiming wants to save the drug testers being used as an expendable resource, but she's in a bad situation herself. She'll have to find another way.

5140118.name: The Art of War
5140118.tips: Zhiming finds a way to earn Seema's trust while getting closer to the drug testers, and begins to make her opening move.

5140119.name: Unknown Strategy
5140119.tips: Azim stirs up trouble during an experiment, and the drug testers' mindset shifts.

5140120.name: Step One: Observe
5140120.tips: The appearance of Kumar shows Zhiming a new possibility, and a plan to turn the tide forms in her mind.

5140121.name: Step Two: Analyze
5140121.tips: To overcome her massive disadvantage, Zhiming is forced to face an unavoidable sacrifice.

5140122.name: Step Three: Deduce
5140122.tips: Zhiming earns Seema's trust during the experiment, while Kumar is given the cold shoulder.

5140123.name: Step Four: Act
5140123.tips: After getting a clearer picture of Seema and Ravana's thinking, Zhiming puts her escape plan into action.

5140124.name: Fear of Loss
5140124.tips: Letting go of her elaborate calculations, Zhiming returns to her Modifier's heart and ultimately chooses to put herself at risk.

5140125.name: Pride of Gain
5140125.tips: Luwu, Zhiming, and Kali take on Ravana together. Who will manage to turn the tide?

5140126.name: Uncertain Outcome
5140126.tips: The storm in the slums settles, but perhaps it's the start of a bigger one brewing in Shashvat...

5191001.name: Lost in the Light
5191001.tips: The light, never-dimming, shines through the fog, pointing the way back to port for every lost ship.

5191002.name: The Town in the Fog
5191002.tips: The solitary island is shrouded in a shadow known as "The Divine," and yet the knight's name is covered in dust.

5191003.name: Trail of Disturbance
5191003.tips: The vague clues are like water flowing through the palm of one's hand, eluding any attempt to grasp them. The actions of the many are mixed and intertwined, obscuring the truth from light.

5191004.name: Nightsong Robin
5191004.tips: Was the voyage at the height of the storm a coincidence or a part of a nefarious scheme? The missing target has finally appeared, albeit with their weapon aimed at their former companions.

5191005.name: Undertow
5191005.tips: The young man has no time to face their emotions right now, not when a spider web of dark undercurrents is lurking out there in the thick fog.

5191006.name: White Waters
5191006.tips: The ship sails into a sea devoid of light as wandering souls linger in the deserted town. The white curse bares its fangs in the dark night after its long wait.

5191007.name: Enemy Tide
5191007.tips: The brilliant glory from a century before is still protecting the coast a hundred years later, though admittedly shakily. The white enemy troops are like an endless tsunami, ready to swallow up this fragile island at any time.

5191008.name: Song of the Moon
5191008.tips: The candle is snuffed out in the cold wind of betrayal, and the bright moon rises above the beleaguered city. As the distant song sounds, it's time to deal with the white blade and crimson blood.

5191009.name: A Past Impossible to Break Free of
5191009.tips: Obsessed and trapped in the memories of the past, and holding on to a love that should have been forgotten a long time ago only to find that said love has long gone bad when the shell of hope is finally broken.

5191010.name: A Sight That Should Never Have Existed in the First Place
5191010.tips: The door leading to the abyss is ajar, revealing a sight that should never have existed here in the first place. And behind the door lurks a figure that shouldn't be here either.

5191011.name: A Face That Should Never Have Reappeared
5191011.tips: An erroneous retention has ultimately led to a wrong rebirth. Somewhere between the sky and the sea, the god who was forced to be born bears a sad face.

5191012.name: No Way to Retreat
5191012.tips: The invading demons are a sea of pure white, and the human city is in ruins and hovering on the line between life and death. What can be done about the incoming enemy tide?

5191013.name: No Way to Advance
5191013.tips: The longswords are broken, and the heavy cannons have fallen silent. How can lone soldiers with their wings clipped defeat an inaccessible enemy?

5191014.name: In a Shining Manner
5191014.tips: Night always eventually comes to an end, and the sun always inevitably rises.

5191015.name: In the Name of the Lighthouse
5191015.tips: The cutting light of the waning moon brings the hunt under the night sky to an end, and the flame of the rising sun brings forth a brand new tomorrow.

5191016.name: Returning and Going
5191016.tips: Civilization will find new life in the rubble, and the earth's scars will heal over time. Some people will stay, some will leave, and all for the same thing: the final answer.

5191017.name: Turing's Shadow
5191017.tips: Behind all that darkness, the shadows themselves are also wrangling with each other.

5191018.name: A Rift in Cooperation
5191018.tips: The seeds of betrayal were planted the moment the game started.
